testcase.name: Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials urlencode values in GET params (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials construct URL properly with base query parameters (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials a 400 should give an InvalidRequestError with http status, body, and JSON body
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials a 401 should give an AuthenticationError with http status, body, and JSON body
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials a 402 should give a CardError with http status, body, and JSON body
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials a 404 should give an InvalidRequestError with http status, body, and JSON body
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials setting a nil value for a param should exclude that param from the request (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials requesting with a unicode ID should result in a request
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials requesting with no ID should result in an InvalidRequestError with no request
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials making a GET request with parameters should have a query string and no body (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials making a POST request with parameters should have a body and no query string (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials loading an object should issue a GET request
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials using array accessors should be the same as the method interface (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials accessing a property other than id or parent on an unfetched object should fetch it (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials updating an object should issue a POST request with only the changed properties (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials updating should merge in returned properties (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials deleting should send no props and result in an object that has no props other deleted (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials loading an object with properties that have specific types should instantiate those classes (PENDING)
Nurego::ApiResource with valid credentials loading all of an APIResource should return an array of recursively instantiated objects (PENDING)
